Diacron Group is an international finance consulting company which provides professional financial services to overseas Enterprises investing abroad. Its headquarters are in Europe, and have other offices in other continents.
The financial firm is a fast growing consulting company that provides services include:
1.Tax planning strategy during the FIE set up in China;
2.Consulting on Chinese and international tax issues;
3.Accounting outsourcing;
4.Consulting on foreign exchange matters;
5.Internal and external audit services;
6.Financial Due Diligence for M&A projects.
7.IFRS compliance.
Due to its fast expanding business, it is now looking for new talents to employ in its China practice. A competitive package and excellent career development opportunities are guaranteed to those outstanding candidates that will qualify for the position.
